    "body": "Reasoning: I find myself sometimes needing to know where an injections is, without needing to know it's content.",
    "closed_at": "2026-04-13T14:28:56Z",
    "comment_data": [],
    "comment_regular_data": [
        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": ">  I find myself sometimes needing to know where an injections is, without needing to know it's content.\n\nWhy?",
