        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "In incremental selection: not really, around 3-9+x faster (tested on `emacs/src/xdisp.c`, select all and change text, ~900ms before, after: ~300ms on first parse, much much faster on second (<100ms)).\r\nIn ultimate autopair: strongly needed. Same numbers as above, but need to repase on \"every\" key-press...",
